_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		  </table>\r\n</div>Looking down the Flett Glacier<br>\r\r\n<br>\r\r\nJust watch out for the sharp rocks if you fall – Anastasia drew first blood from her rump after slipping off one of the boulders :-)<br>\r\r\n<br>\r\r\n<div class=\"photonormal\">\r\n<table valign=\"top\" border=\"0\" width=\"626\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"sdw_box\">\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/top_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_top\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/top_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_left\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_body\" width=\"600\"><div>\r\n<a href=\"javascript:photoZoom(\'Mjs7ND85ISIk\')\" title=\"Click to enlarge\"><img src=\"http://www.supertopo.com/photos/9/18/213303_17925_L.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"386\" name=\"\" alt=\"\"></a><span class=\"small\"><div class=\"photo-credit\">Credit: PellucidWombat</div></span>\r\n</div></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_right\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_bottom\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		  </table>\r\n</div>Bouldering on the Boulder in My Nepal Evos<br>\r\r\n<br>\r\r\n<div class=\"photonormal\">\r\n<table valign=\"top\" border=\"0\" width=\"626\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"sdw_box\">\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/top_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_top\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/top_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_left\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_body\" width=\"600\"><div>\r\n<a href=\"javascript:photoZoom(\'Mjs7ND82KCkl\')\" title=\"Click to enlarge\"><img src=\"http://www.supertopo.com/photos/9/18/213304_14279_L.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" name=\"\" alt=\"\"></a><span class=\"small\"><div class=\"photo-credit\">Credit: PellucidWombat</div></span>\r\n</div></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_right\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_bottom\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		  </table>\r\n</div>Anastasia Doing the Best Problem that I Found on the Boulders<br>\r\r\n<br>\r\r\n<div class=\"photonormal\">\r\n<table valign=\"top\" border=\"0\" width=\"626\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"sdw_box\">\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/top_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_top\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/top_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_left\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_body\" width=\"600\"><div>\r\n<a href=\"javascript:photoZoom(\'Mjs7NDw8JiIq\')\" title=\"Click to enlarge\"><img src=\"http://www.supertopo.com/photos/9/18/213305_30584_L.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"443\" name=\"\" alt=\"\"></a><span class=\"small\"><div class=\"photo-credit\">Credit: PellucidWombat</div></span>\r\n</div></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_right\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_bottom\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		  </table>\r\n</div>Perfect Photo Op<br>\r\r\n<br>\r\r\n<br>\r\r\nAnastasia chose to spend the rest of the day relaxing at camp while I spazzed out and ran further up the ridge, camera in tow. <br>\r\r\n<br>\r\r\n<div class=\"photonormal\">\r\n<table valign=\"top\" border=\"0\" width=\"626\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"sdw_box\">\r\n			<tr>\r\n	