rities almost ended my climb prematurely.<br><div class=\"photo-credit\">Credit: PellucidWombat</div></span>\r\n</div></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_right\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_bottom\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		  </table>\r\n</div>I appealed to the authorities, giving a heartfelt defense of my lofty goals in hopes that they would allow me to continue reaching for the sky. Fortunately my explanation of what I was doing worked, as the concerned grounds manager eventually relented, saying \"eh. I guess this is Berkeley.\"<br>\r\r\n<br>\r\r\n<div class=\"photonormal\">\r\n<table valign=\"top\" border=\"0\" width=\"626\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"sdw_box\">\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/top_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_top\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/top_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_left\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_body\" width=\"600\"><div>\r\n<a href=\"javascript:photoZoom(\'Mjo1Ozc3ICMl\')\" title=\"Click to enlarge\"><img src=\"http://www.supertopo.com/photos/9/49/216444_11658_L.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"599\" name=\"\" alt=\"And so, refreshed from lunch, I pressed on with renewed vigor.\"></a><span class=\"small\"><br>And so, refreshed from lunch, I pressed on with renewed vigor.<br><div class=\"photo-credit\">Credit: PellucidWombat</div></span>\r\n</div></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_right\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n			<tr>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_left_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			  <td class=\"sdw_bottom\"></td>\r\n			  <td><img src=\"/nav_img/bottom_right_sdw.gif\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\"></td>\r\n			</tr>\r\n		  </table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"photonormal\">\r\n<table 